Interface ActionInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Action, AttackAction, ChantingAction, CraftAction, DieAction, DoNothingAction, DropAction, DropItemAction, EatFoodAction, FertilizeAction, HarvestAction, KickAction, MoveActorAction, PickUpItemAction, ReloadAction, ShotgunAimMenuAction, ShotgunShootAction, SniperRifleAimAction, SniperRifleAimMenuAction, SniperRifleShootAction, SniperRifleShootMenuAction, SowAction, SpecialAction, SpitBehaviour, TransfterAction, WindowSmashAction, ZombieExpressionAction
public interface ActionInterface
This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.
